      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "At the trades council meeting last\nnight the retail grocers' clerks pre-\nscented their schedule for another\nyear for approval by the council. IT\ninvolves no raise In wages. asking\nsimply recognition of the union and\nthe establishment of the same hours\nof labor as last year.\n\n\nThe Bartenders' League of America\nalso presented its agreement for ap-\nproval. 1t involves simply recogni-\nton of the union by employers and an\nagreement to hire none but union\nmen.\n\n\nThe leather workers asked that the\nA. A. Kraft company. jobbers in har-\nness and saddlery. be put ON the I'M\nfair list for refusal to employ mem\nbers of the union and pay the union\nscale."
    }
  ]
